  "texts": [
    "For each poem, we automatically generate a short human-style prompt using GPT-5 and treat the original poem as the expert demonstration.",
    "Out of the 40k poems, we reserve 256 poems at random as our test set.",
    "Since poetry writing does not admit an objective verifier, we evaluate RARO and baselines using GPT-5.",
    "Specifically, we set up two evaluation metrics: scalar score and win-rate.",
    "The scalar score is measured by prompting GPT-5 to score the poem on a scale of 1-7 then normalized to 0-100, considering both prompt adherence and literary quality."
  ],
